Product description

The original and all-around great tasting snack. With 25% less sugar than other leading juice drinks*, plus no artificial colors, flavors, or preservatives, it’s still the fave of moms and kids alike.

From the manufacturer

A splash of mixed fruit flavors from all natural ingredients create flavorful kids juices for every occasion.

Our ready to drink juice offers a convenient way for kids to hydrate on the go.

Seeing is believing. Every Capri Sun Juice is packaged in a clear bottom pouch so you can see the goodness inside.
